#
# Revision 1.12  2003/02/28 18:46:37  pwagner
# Links utctotai library
#
# Revision 1.11  2002/11/25 21:21:02  pwagner
# gcc_version to allow building with Lahey on gcc post 2.96
#
# Revision 1.10  2002/09/06 00:09:07  pwagner
# BLAS can now bring in more than a single
#
